You're such an inspiration for me, my hero. 
He's a nice person, loveable person, caring, and independent person. 
He always teach me about being nice to other people. Always mad to someone who hurt us. Take care of us. Makes us his number one priorities. Always trying to fullfill what we need, he never said no to us, even when he can't give it now he said "later" and then he always keep his promises. Never broke it.
He's the one who always make me feel proud, an amazing person. I always astonished about¬† his life. Every inch of his life is amazing. I always want to look like him. 
He never stop working hard for us, even he felt tired he never show it to us. 
Sometimes he get hard on us, but I know it for makes us a better person. 
He's the reason that I tried really hard for life, the reason behind my smile.
I felt sorry and full of regret that I still can't make him happy and proud. I'm sorry that I often let him down, make he felt disappointed. Sorry. 
But God loves him, so God take him first.
Even now his gone, and I can't see his face anymore. But still I will keep my best to make him happy and proud from up there. 
I hope God give a best place on there. 
He's the man that I love the most more than anything in this entire world.
